WEBVTT

1
00:00:28.917 --> 00:00:32.875
Once upon a time,

2
00:00:32.958 --> 00:00:38.333
there was a duel between Arjuna and Karna.

3
00:00:51.833 --> 00:00:56.000
<i>Events and outcomes in life are shaped</i>

4
00:00:56.083 --> 00:00:59.292
<i>by the choices and decisions we make.</i>

5
00:01:00.125 --> 00:01:02.167
<i>I was born to a wayang puppeteer.</i>

6
00:01:09.667 --> 00:01:12.500
<i>Since birth, my destiny has been decided.</i>

7
00:01:13.917 --> 00:01:17.417
<i>My ancestor came from the past
to determine my fate.</i>

8
00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:22.208
Name your son

9
00:01:22.292 --> 00:01:25.417
I Made Budiawan.

10
00:01:26.250 --> 00:01:32.458
Because he is

11
00:01:32.542 --> 00:01:35.708
the seventh heir.

12
00:01:35.792 --> 00:01:40.375
Inherited the skill of being

13
00:01:40.458 --> 00:01:45.000
a wayang puppeteer from our ancestors.

14
00:01:45.083 --> 00:01:48.250
And teach him the craft
of being a puppeteer.

15
00:01:49.625 --> 00:01:52.625
<i>They also have chosen who
I'm going to marry in the future.</i>

16
00:01:52.708 --> 00:01:54.833
<i>Her name is Putu.</i>

17
00:01:54.917 --> 00:01:58.125
<i>The daughter of a respected elder
in our village.</i>

18
00:01:58.208 --> 00:02:01.500
<i>But one day, this girl came to my village.</i>

19
00:02:03.958 --> 00:02:05.458
<i>Her name is Niluh.</i>

20
00:02:05.542 --> 00:02:07.417
<i>She has Balinese and Japanese ancestry.</i>

21
00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:10.667
Hello.

22
00:02:10.750 --> 00:02:12.458
- Made.
- Niluh.

23
00:02:17.750 --> 00:02:19.708
<i>Niluh is a unique person.</i>

24
00:02:19.792 --> 00:02:21.792
<i>She doesn't like to be controlled.</i>

25
00:02:23.625 --> 00:02:26.958
<i>She's a free spirit, like the starling,</i>

26
00:02:27.042 --> 00:02:30.875
<i>her favorite bird</i>
<i>that she named Mukudori</i>-chan.

27
00:02:32.667 --> 00:02:35.250
- Thank you, Mukudori<i>-chan.</i>
- Niluh, don't!

28
00:02:36.583 --> 00:02:39.000
Goodbye, Mukudori<i>-chan!</i>

29
00:02:45.583 --> 00:02:47.000
- See you tomorrow!
- See you!

30
00:03:01.333 --> 00:03:02.833
Sorry for keeping you waiting!

31
00:03:02.917 --> 00:03:03.958
Order's up!

32
00:03:04.792 --> 00:03:06.417
For the guests at Table 12!

33
00:03:13.375 --> 00:03:15.458
Kids, don't run around.

34
00:03:15.542 --> 00:03:16.542
Be careful!

35
00:03:21.667 --> 00:03:23.958
<i>Niluh taught me new stuff,</i>

36
00:03:24.042 --> 00:03:26.875
<i>such as bothering her dad
in his sushi restaurant.</i>

37
00:03:31.208 --> 00:03:34.167
<i>Or dressing up in cosplay
where she would be the heroine,</i>

38
00:03:34.250 --> 00:03:38.500
<i>and I would be the villain
who's afraid of heights.</i>

39
00:03:46.458 --> 00:03:48.708
Come on, scaredy-cat. Jump down here!

40
00:03:48.792 --> 00:03:49.875
But it's too high.

41
00:03:50.417 --> 00:03:51.917
Scaredy-cat.

42
00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.708
- Jump down here!
- It's too high!

43
00:03:53.792 --> 00:03:55.500
Come on, jump down here!

44
00:03:57.667 --> 00:04:01.833
<i>Oh, and by the way,
she sewed the blue robe herself.</i>

45
00:04:15.417 --> 00:04:16.625
I'm stuck.

46
00:04:18.792 --> 00:04:22.083
No idea what to write for
the Japanese-influenced music.

47
00:04:23.333 --> 00:04:25.417
Need some Japanese music for reference?

48
00:04:26.333 --> 00:04:28.583
I have some Japanese records.

49
00:04:29.208 --> 00:04:31.625
- You can borrow them.
- Are you sure?

50
00:04:32.417 --> 00:04:34.583
- Can I?
- Of course.

51
00:04:40.792 --> 00:04:44.375
<i>Two-thirds of my life were spent with her.</i>

52
00:04:44.458 --> 00:04:47.292
<i>- She knew everything about me.</i>
- See you tomorrow?

53
00:04:47.917 --> 00:04:49.333
See you tomorrow!

54
00:04:57.667 --> 00:05:02.083
<i>Including my fear of riding in vehicles
because of this damn minibus.</i>

55
00:05:07.042 --> 00:05:07.958
Kadek.

56
00:05:08.042 --> 00:05:11.083
<i>That's why I now have to take
motion sickness medicine</i>

57
00:05:11.167 --> 00:05:15.250
<i>wherever I go so I can
sleep through the entire trip.</i>

58
00:05:16.042 --> 00:05:18.542
Tie him up.

59
00:05:21.333 --> 00:05:23.708
<i>And Niluh is the only one
with the patience</i>

60
00:05:23.792 --> 00:05:25.500
<i>to take me everywhere.</i>

61
00:05:26.875 --> 00:05:28.750
Hurry up!

62
00:05:30.375 --> 00:05:31.417
Hurry up!

63
00:05:41.833 --> 00:05:43.083
Turn right!

64
00:05:48.042 --> 00:05:49.750
<i>Even Kadek and Wayan,</i>

65
00:05:49.833 --> 00:05:53.583
<i>my so-called "best friends,"
wouldn't let me ride with them.</i>

66
00:05:53.667 --> 00:05:55.625
Did he take his motion sickness pill?

67
00:05:55.708 --> 00:05:56.792
I don't know.

68
00:05:56.875 --> 00:05:58.292
I think Niluh gave him one.

69
00:05:59.375 --> 00:06:01.208
It's good he trusts her to bring him.

70
00:06:01.292 --> 00:06:04.458
Or he'd be walking everywhere.

71
00:06:07.792 --> 00:06:10.167
<i>That's how close I am with Niluh.</i>

72
00:06:10.250 --> 00:06:13.625
<i>So it's only natural for me
to be afraid of losing her.</i>

73
00:06:25.250 --> 00:06:28.542
<i>It's been a few days</i>

74
00:06:28.625 --> 00:06:33.417
<i>Into the journey</i>

75
00:06:35.458 --> 00:06:38.875
Now he will.

76
00:06:39.542 --> 00:06:40.833
Do you want to try?

77
00:06:40.917 --> 00:06:42.333
- Yes, Dad.
- Here you go.

78
00:06:43.958 --> 00:06:50.958
<i>It's been a few days into the journey</i>

79
00:07:01.083 --> 00:07:02.208
I want to talk to you.

80
00:07:03.708 --> 00:07:09.208
Your grandmother's health
is declining fast.

81
00:07:09.292 --> 00:07:12.833
The doctor gave her

82
00:07:13.625 --> 00:07:14.917
one year.

83
00:07:16.625 --> 00:07:19.583
Your father wants us to
move to Japan temporarily.

84
00:07:20.292 --> 00:07:22.792
Must I go with you?

85
00:07:22.875 --> 00:07:25.125
Don't you want to be there
for your grandmother

86
00:07:26.042 --> 00:07:27.917
in her remaining time?

87
00:07:29.917 --> 00:07:32.167
Help me take care of your grandmother.

88
00:07:32.250 --> 00:07:34.417
Your father is the only child she has.

89
00:07:34.917 --> 00:07:37.375
We are the only family she has.

90
00:07:38.875 --> 00:07:43.417
But I'm waiting for the acceptance letter
from Dewata University.

91
00:07:44.875 --> 00:07:46.375
You can study in Japan.

92
00:07:47.042 --> 00:07:49.042
There are many good universities in Tokyo.

93
00:07:53.167 --> 00:07:54.375
Let's do this.

94
00:07:55.875 --> 00:07:59.792
If Dewata University
approves your scholarship,

95
00:08:00.375 --> 00:08:02.000
we can have another conversation.

96
00:08:04.333 --> 00:08:09.333
But for the time being, we have to
make preparations to move to Japan.

97
00:08:21.333 --> 00:08:24.167
I know the timing is bad,
but the sooner the better.

98
00:08:26.458 --> 00:08:27.458
It's gonna be okay.

99
00:08:34.542 --> 00:08:35.542
Luh?

100
00:08:36.458 --> 00:08:37.458
Niluh?

101
00:08:40.750 --> 00:08:41.833
Niluh!

102
00:08:58.417 --> 00:08:59.417
Niluh?

103
00:09:00.708 --> 00:09:01.708
Luh?

104
00:09:03.875 --> 00:09:05.042
Hey, what's wrong?

105
00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.000
My parents and I are moving to Japan.

106
00:09:21.958 --> 00:09:23.750
My grandmother is gravely ill.

107
00:09:29.125 --> 00:09:30.125
What?

108
00:09:32.333 --> 00:09:34.125
But this is your hometown.

109
00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:37.917
That's my hometown too.

110
00:09:39.375 --> 00:09:40.667
What about me?

111
00:09:42.667 --> 00:09:43.667
You are…

112
00:09:44.042 --> 00:09:45.542
You're gonna be okay.

113
00:09:47.875 --> 00:09:49.792
I mean, what about us?

114
00:09:51.542 --> 00:09:52.958
There is no "us."

115
00:09:55.042 --> 00:09:56.292
How can you say that?

116
00:09:58.750 --> 00:09:59.875
But it's true.

117
00:10:02.542 --> 00:10:04.042
I thought we were friends.

118
00:10:04.542 --> 00:10:07.542
That doesn't mean
we can't still be friends.

119
00:10:42.875 --> 00:10:44.625
But it's not definitive.

120
00:10:49.208 --> 00:10:53.958
If Dewata University accepts
my application, I'll study here.

121
00:10:56.083 --> 00:10:58.083
But what if you're not accepted?

122
00:11:24.042 --> 00:11:25.875
I can't imagine…

123
00:11:30.875 --> 00:11:32.833
looking at your house…

124
00:11:37.875 --> 00:11:40.292
And not seeing you in the window.

125
00:12:32.333 --> 00:12:34.167
May you be blessed, ma'am.

126
00:12:34.250 --> 00:12:36.542
May you be blessed too.

127
00:12:38.083 --> 00:12:39.000
How are you?

128
00:12:39.083 --> 00:12:40.917
We're fine, thank you.

129
00:12:43.583 --> 00:12:46.667
Here's a little gift from Semarang.

130
00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:48.542
- Thank you.
- Welcome.

131
00:12:48.625 --> 00:12:50.375
Thank you.

132
00:12:51.208 --> 00:12:54.333
- May you be blessed.
- May you be blessed too.

133
00:12:54.417 --> 00:12:57.208
- You've become more beautiful.
- You're just saying that.

134
00:12:57.292 --> 00:12:59.875
- Please, come in.
- Let's go inside.

135
00:13:03.167 --> 00:13:06.125
Made, I heard you like making music.

136
00:13:06.625 --> 00:13:08.792
- Yes, I do.
- Is it done?

137
00:13:09.458 --> 00:13:10.625
Wanna to listen to it?

138
00:13:12.250 --> 00:13:14.917
Do you still make content
for your social media?

139
00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:18.292
Yeah. Actually, I just got a new gig.

140
00:13:18.375 --> 00:13:21.000
Creating a promo video and product photos.

141
00:13:21.083 --> 00:13:23.042
Great. How about we go to my studio?

142
00:13:23.125 --> 00:13:24.583
- Okay.
- Let's go.

143
00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:37.000
What do you think?

144
00:13:37.792 --> 00:13:38.792
Do you like it?

145
00:13:39.417 --> 00:13:42.833
Maybe you can use it for the music score
in your content.

146
00:13:44.542 --> 00:13:46.500
But it's too grand for my liking.

147
00:13:47.958 --> 00:13:52.458
Can you make it more Japanese-style?

148
00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:56.667
I thought the same thing too.

149
00:13:57.458 --> 00:14:01.542
I'll send you the song when it's ready.

150
00:14:16.042 --> 00:14:18.583
Can you come to the set
when we start filming?

151
00:14:19.542 --> 00:14:22.917
Of course, I'll be there.

152
00:14:23.958 --> 00:14:28.000
I won't let you be alone during filming.

153
00:14:33.083 --> 00:14:34.375
Thank you.

154
00:15:03.792 --> 00:15:05.292
Hey, Shiro!

155
00:15:06.125 --> 00:15:07.125
Hey!

156
00:15:07.667 --> 00:15:09.208
You startled me!

157
00:15:13.292 --> 00:15:17.417
Luh, you don't have
any plans tomorrow, right?

158
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.792
I don't? Sotoy!

159
00:15:20.875 --> 00:15:23.750
What? That's delicious. I love it!

160
00:15:23.833 --> 00:15:25.917
- You love what?
- Sotoy!

161
00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:28.875
Chicken so toy, Goat so toy.
Especially the spicy one.

162
00:15:30.583 --> 00:15:32.333
You're silly!

163
00:15:32.417 --> 00:15:33.792
I'm serious.

164
00:15:33.875 --> 00:15:38.167
You should skip school
and go to the Kite Festival with me.

165
00:15:39.042 --> 00:15:42.000
To watch or to participate?

166
00:15:42.083 --> 00:15:43.375
To participate, of course.

167
00:15:44.708 --> 00:15:47.333
Who else is coming
and how will we get there?

168
00:15:49.125 --> 00:15:50.375
The usual.

169
00:15:50.458 --> 00:15:54.083
You, me, Kadek, Wayan.

170
00:15:55.333 --> 00:15:56.542
I'll ride the bike.

171
00:15:57.417 --> 00:15:59.333
You can go with Kadek and Wayan.

172
00:16:00.500 --> 00:16:02.083
Okay, it's a deal.

173
00:16:07.792 --> 00:16:10.250
I'm going back to Jakarta
Want anything, babe?

174
00:16:13.792 --> 00:16:15.250
Putu is going to Jakarta.

175
00:16:17.458 --> 00:16:19.250
She asked if I want something.

176
00:16:20.375 --> 00:16:21.583
Any ideas?

177
00:16:23.125 --> 00:16:26.458
How should I know? How about the Monas?

178
00:16:28.833 --> 00:16:30.083
I'm not joking.

179
00:16:35.792 --> 00:16:37.792
She's going for a costume fitting.

180
00:16:37.875 --> 00:16:39.208
It's for the promo video.

181
00:16:39.708 --> 00:16:40.708
Cool, huh?

182
00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:45.875
Beats me. Can you just leave?

183
00:16:46.500 --> 00:16:47.500
Go home.

184
00:16:49.208 --> 00:16:50.208
What did I do?

185
00:16:52.042 --> 00:16:53.042
I'm sleepy!

186
00:17:05.333 --> 00:17:06.333
Made!

187
00:17:06.875 --> 00:17:07.875
Luh!

188
00:17:09.167 --> 00:17:10.167
Made!

189
00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:12.000
Yes!

190
00:17:14.750 --> 00:17:15.750
Niluh!

191
00:17:19.875 --> 00:17:21.875
- Careful.
- Yes.

192
00:17:21.958 --> 00:17:23.167
Don't forget the thread.

193
00:17:24.292 --> 00:17:25.500
- Here.
- Great.

194
00:17:29.417 --> 00:17:31.500
- Hey.
- Niluh!

195
00:17:34.500 --> 00:17:35.750
It's already secured.

196
00:17:45.375 --> 00:17:48.458
Guys, I'm riding along with Made.

197
00:17:49.125 --> 00:17:50.125
Later.

198
00:17:52.250 --> 00:17:54.417
- I envy him.
- Me too.

199
00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:55.833
No, you're not.

200
00:17:55.917 --> 00:17:57.083
Let's go.

201
00:18:08.167 --> 00:18:09.792
You're not going with them?

202
00:18:10.625 --> 00:18:11.917
It's better with the bike.

203
00:18:13.125 --> 00:18:14.125
Okay.

204
00:18:19.708 --> 00:18:21.083
How is your music going?

205
00:18:23.875 --> 00:18:24.875
I don't know.

206
00:18:25.792 --> 00:18:26.792
Still blank.

207
00:18:29.042 --> 00:18:30.042
Here.

208
00:18:35.625 --> 00:18:36.917
I've been looking for this.

209
00:18:38.875 --> 00:18:40.917
- Thank you.
- Sure.

210
00:18:41.625 --> 00:18:43.375
I went to your house last night.

211
00:18:44.167 --> 00:18:45.583
I wanted to give it to you.

212
00:19:01.583 --> 00:19:02.917
Look at those.

213
00:19:06.167 --> 00:19:08.167
It's called a Jangan kite.

214
00:19:08.250 --> 00:19:09.792
I think that one's a winner.

215
00:19:10.875 --> 00:19:13.333
The one on the left?

216
00:19:13.417 --> 00:19:15.833
I like the white
and red stripes over there.

217
00:19:17.375 --> 00:19:20.292
- May you be blessed.
- May you be blessed too.

218
00:19:20.375 --> 00:19:24.708
If you want to fly your kite, we provide
a less crowded site right there.

219
00:19:24.792 --> 00:19:25.792
If you don't mind.

220
00:19:25.833 --> 00:19:27.208
- Okay.
- Okay.

221
00:19:27.292 --> 00:19:29.083
- Thank you, sir.
- Okay.

222
00:19:39.375 --> 00:19:42.583
Kadek, you stay here
and hold the kite with him.

223
00:19:42.667 --> 00:19:44.500
I'll go help Niluh with the thread.

224
00:19:44.583 --> 00:19:46.958
- How about the other way around?
- No, it's okay.

225
00:19:47.042 --> 00:19:48.208
I really don't mind.

226
00:19:50.375 --> 00:19:52.667
That is exactly why you need to act fast.

227
00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:55.917
Let's count to three
and pull the thread together, okay?

228
00:19:56.625 --> 00:20:00.208
One, two, three!

229
00:20:03.542 --> 00:20:04.542
We did it!

230
00:20:44.667 --> 00:20:46.625
- It's good, right?
- Yeah, I like it.

231
00:20:59.208 --> 00:21:01.625
Look, I think
Niluh's bike has a flat tire.

232
00:21:02.333 --> 00:21:03.333
Really?

233
00:21:04.958 --> 00:21:06.000
It does.

234
00:21:06.583 --> 00:21:08.250
We'll carry it on our wagon.

235
00:21:15.625 --> 00:21:16.750
Watch out for the wing.

236
00:21:17.375 --> 00:21:18.375
Hi!

237
00:21:20.500 --> 00:21:23.417
I can't believe you're here too.

238
00:21:25.000 --> 00:21:26.625
Are you here alone?

239
00:21:27.333 --> 00:21:29.417
- Hello, Putu!
- Hello, Putu!

240
00:21:29.500 --> 00:21:31.208
No, with Kadek and Wayan too.

241
00:21:32.292 --> 00:21:33.583
Let's hang out.

242
00:21:38.667 --> 00:21:40.375
No, it's okay.

243
00:21:41.250 --> 00:21:42.250
Are you sure?

244
00:21:42.750 --> 00:21:44.625
- Yeah, you can go.
- Don't worry.

245
00:21:47.250 --> 00:21:48.958
Shall we leave now?

246
00:21:49.042 --> 00:21:51.458
- How about Made?
- Don't ask me.

247
00:21:56.292 --> 00:21:58.917
- Are you gonna be okay?
- Of course.

248
00:22:02.292 --> 00:22:03.292
Let's go.

249
00:22:04.833 --> 00:22:06.333
There's a new café nearby.

250
00:22:06.417 --> 00:22:08.458
Why aren't we moving? I need a bath.

251
00:22:57.292 --> 00:22:59.917
- Can I have an autograph?
- Are you both dating?

252
00:23:03.083 --> 00:23:04.083
Is he your boyfriend?

253
00:23:07.667 --> 00:23:09.167
Thank you.

254
00:23:09.250 --> 00:23:12.125
I'm sorry if they made you uncomfortable.

255
00:23:13.958 --> 00:23:15.833
I don't mind.

256
00:23:15.917 --> 00:23:18.292
I know who you are.

257
00:23:19.583 --> 00:23:20.583
Delicious?

258
00:23:24.583 --> 00:23:28.333
Can you go with me
to a product launch event tomorrow?

259
00:23:28.417 --> 00:23:29.417
Can you?

260
00:23:30.292 --> 00:23:32.500
Miss Putu, can I post the video?

261
00:23:32.583 --> 00:23:35.458
Who knows, maybe it'll go viral.

262
00:23:35.542 --> 00:23:36.542
Sure.

263
00:23:37.583 --> 00:23:40.292
