Praise the Lord, I'm fine.

535
00:42:55.667 --> 00:42:57.833
- And you?
- I'm fine too.

536
00:42:57.917 --> 00:42:58.917
This is Genzo.

537
00:42:59.000 --> 00:43:01.458
Hello, I'm Niluh.

538
00:43:01.542 --> 00:43:03.125
Hi, I'm Genzo.

539
00:43:03.208 --> 00:43:04.250
Welcome to Bali.

540
00:43:04.333 --> 00:43:05.333
Thank you.

541
00:43:05.375 --> 00:43:06.375
Let's go inside.

542
00:43:06.917 --> 00:43:07.917
Bye!

543
00:43:08.000 --> 00:43:09.875
Do you have a boyfriend?

544
00:43:09.958 --> 00:43:12.500
<i>In the midst of
my already complicated life,</i>

545
00:43:12.583 --> 00:43:14.000
<i>two more people came along</i>

546
00:43:14.083 --> 00:43:17.417
<i>who would later worsen my headache.</i>

547
00:43:24.792 --> 00:43:26.500
- Uncle.
- Keiko?

548
00:43:26.583 --> 00:43:28.208
Yes. Uncle!

549
00:43:28.292 --> 00:43:29.458
Keiko!

550
00:43:29.542 --> 00:43:30.542
<i>Her name is Keiko.</i>

551
00:43:30.583 --> 00:43:31.583
How are you?

552
00:43:31.667 --> 00:43:32.667
<i>She's Niluh's cousin.</i>

553
00:43:32.750 --> 00:43:35.875
<i>They say she'd help her uncle
and his family moving back to Japan.</i>

554
00:43:35.958 --> 00:43:36.792
It was great.

555
00:43:36.917 --> 00:43:38.833
<i>The problem is not with Keiko.</i>

556
00:43:38.917 --> 00:43:41.583
- Auntie Padma!
<i>- The problem is with…</i>

557
00:43:41.667 --> 00:43:45.792
- You look so pretty!
- You're just saying that.

558
00:43:45.875 --> 00:43:47.083
<i>…this man.</i>

559
00:43:47.167 --> 00:43:48.958
<i>His name is Genzo.</i>

560
00:43:49.042 --> 00:43:51.708
I'm teaching
the Indonesian language in Tokyo.

561
00:43:52.500 --> 00:43:53.958
That's wonderful!

562
00:43:54.042 --> 00:43:56.750
Incredible! You teach Indonesian
as a side job?

563
00:43:56.833 --> 00:43:57.833
What's your real job?

564
00:43:59.458 --> 00:44:01.458
I work as a voice actor in anime.

565
00:44:02.792 --> 00:44:03.958
Anime?

566
00:44:04.625 --> 00:44:06.833
Like in <i>Gundam?</i> Or <i>Naruto?</i>

567
00:44:06.917 --> 00:44:08.208
Yes, like those anime.

568
00:44:08.292 --> 00:44:10.208
Incredible!

569
00:44:11.417 --> 00:44:12.292
Boyfriend?

570
00:44:12.375 --> 00:44:13.375
Sir, ma'am…

571
00:44:13.458 --> 00:44:15.542
Hello. My name is Genzo.

572
00:44:15.625 --> 00:44:16.833
Nice to meet you.

573
00:44:16.917 --> 00:44:18.875
Genzo is the manager at my office.

574
00:44:18.958 --> 00:44:20.667
Manager?

575
00:44:21.250 --> 00:44:23.792
Mr. Manager, please guide her in her work.

576
00:44:23.875 --> 00:44:24.708
Yes, sir.

577
00:44:24.792 --> 00:44:27.500
- Does he speak Indonesian?
- He does.

578
00:44:28.167 --> 00:44:31.542
He often visits Indonesia on vacation.

579
00:44:33.167 --> 00:44:34.417
It's a hot country, right?

580
00:44:34.500 --> 00:44:37.375
- Let's drink tea, okay?
- Thank you.

581
00:44:37.458 --> 00:44:40.750
Genzo, put your suitcase inside.
You must be exhausted.

582
00:44:40.833 --> 00:44:42.417
Luh, I want to explore the city.

583
00:44:42.500 --> 00:44:44.042
Don't you need a rest?

584
00:44:44.125 --> 00:44:47.083
How many times
have you vacationed in Indonesia?

585
00:44:47.167 --> 00:44:49.875
- Two times.
- I see.

586
00:44:50.542 --> 00:44:53.250
- Do you like it?
- I like it.

587
00:44:53.333 --> 00:44:54.417
It's beautiful, right?

588
00:44:55.375 --> 00:44:57.958
- We don't have that back home.
- In Japan.

589
00:44:58.042 --> 00:44:59.500
- You don't?
- No.

590
00:45:25.000 --> 00:45:27.167
Niluh!

591
00:45:27.958 --> 00:45:29.375
Genzo.

592
00:45:30.042 --> 00:45:32.375
Where are you going?

593
00:45:33.083 --> 00:45:34.708
I'm going to teach dancing.

594
00:45:35.500 --> 00:45:37.458
- Keiko?
- She's already asleep.

595
00:45:41.083 --> 00:45:42.792
Why don't you wear the uniform?

596
00:45:43.375 --> 00:45:46.292
- We didn't know the ceremony is today.
- Wasn't it tomorrow?

597
00:45:46.375 --> 00:45:48.417
- Why didn't you tell us?
- I forgot too.

598
00:45:48.500 --> 00:45:50.167
But you're wearing white.

599
00:45:50.250 --> 00:45:52.917
- It's cream.
- You did it on purpose.

600
00:45:53.000 --> 00:45:55.750
Even if we're different,
as long as the music's in sync,

601
00:45:55.833 --> 00:45:57.083
that's what matters.

602
00:45:58.792 --> 00:46:00.667
Guys, this is Genzo.

603
00:46:00.750 --> 00:46:03.292
He's a friend of my cousin.
He just came from Japan.

604
00:46:03.792 --> 00:46:05.958
Hello, I'm Genzo.

605
00:46:07.458 --> 00:46:09.542
A good-looking guy.

606
00:46:10.208 --> 00:46:11.208
Excuse us.

607
00:46:11.750 --> 00:46:15.000
Genzo<i>-san,</i> you can sit here. Sit here.

608
00:46:15.083 --> 00:46:16.125
- Sure?
- Yeah.

609
00:46:19.750 --> 00:46:20.583
Thank you.

610
00:46:20.667 --> 00:46:22.375
<i>What did I tell you? The problem.</i>

611
00:46:22.458 --> 00:46:23.458
Genzo.

612
00:46:24.708 --> 00:46:25.708
Made.

613
00:46:44.583 --> 00:46:46.083
<i>Keep staring at her.</i>

614
00:47:25.750 --> 00:47:31.125
<i>While Niluh is occupied with Genzo,
I'm occupied with Putu.</i>

615
00:48:03.125 --> 00:48:04.542
Was it exciting?

616
00:48:05.542 --> 00:48:06.542
It was.

617
00:48:09.750 --> 00:48:11.250
Which part do you like most?

618
00:48:12.708 --> 00:48:14.000
Every minute of it.

619
00:48:14.083 --> 00:48:16.042
- Are you sure?
- Yeah.

620
00:48:18.083 --> 00:48:21.917
Do you like the part where I flew?

621
00:48:22.625 --> 00:48:24.042
That's the best part.

622
00:48:30.042 --> 00:48:33.292
How about the part
where I throw Jovan into the sea?

623
00:48:33.375 --> 00:48:34.750
Especially that one!

624
00:48:34.833 --> 00:48:36.833
That's the most funny part, I love it!

625
00:48:41.542 --> 00:48:44.250
We didn't do either of those scenes.

626
00:48:47.542 --> 00:48:48.542
Really?

627
00:48:52.333 --> 00:48:55.417
Were you bored
waiting for me to finish work?

628
00:48:58.042 --> 00:49:02.167
Made, can I ask you something?

629
00:49:03.000 --> 00:49:04.000
Sure.

630
00:49:06.125 --> 00:49:10.042
I want to know how you feel
about our marriage arrangement.

631
00:49:13.500 --> 00:49:14.500
Hey, Made.

632
00:49:15.417 --> 00:49:17.125
Where are you coming from?

633
00:49:19.042 --> 00:49:20.042
From the beach.

634
00:49:22.292 --> 00:49:24.208
We're on our way to grab dinner.

635
00:49:24.292 --> 00:49:25.542
Do you want to come?

636
00:49:27.167 --> 00:49:28.167
Sounds great.

637
00:49:29.000 --> 00:49:30.000
Sure!

638
00:50:02.292 --> 00:50:03.625
Hi.

639
00:50:03.708 --> 00:50:04.708
Hello.

640
00:50:04.792 --> 00:50:06.792
- Please sit down.
- Hi.

641
00:50:06.875 --> 00:50:08.125
Did you wait long?

642
00:50:08.208 --> 00:50:09.917
- Kind of.
- Just a little.

643
00:50:11.500 --> 00:50:14.042
Keiko, what do you do in Japan?

644
00:50:14.125 --> 00:50:16.833
My job is called <i>"seiyu."</i>

645
00:50:16.917 --> 00:50:17.917
What's that?

646
00:50:17.958 --> 00:50:23.208
I'm a voice actor in anime.

647
00:50:24.333 --> 00:50:25.333
Do you like anime?

648
00:50:26.250 --> 00:50:27.250
I love it.

649
00:50:27.292 --> 00:50:31.167
Can you show me how you do <i>"seiyu"?</i>

650
00:50:31.250 --> 00:50:33.708
Of course, but…

651
00:50:34.625 --> 00:50:35.833
Niluh<i>-chan</i> must help me.

652
00:50:36.458 --> 00:50:38.458
No way! I don't want to.

653
00:50:38.542 --> 00:50:39.583
I agree!

654
00:50:39.667 --> 00:50:40.750
Come on, Niluh.

655
00:50:40.833 --> 00:50:43.000
Niluh!

656
00:50:50.625 --> 00:50:53.417
Niluh!

657
00:50:56.500 --> 00:50:57.417
Okay.

658
00:50:57.500 --> 00:50:58.500
Why are you here?

659
00:50:58.583 --> 00:51:01.208
- We've been looking for you.
- Where have you been?

660
00:51:04.208 --> 00:51:08.125
I refuse to go against my principles!

661
00:51:08.208 --> 00:51:10.625
This is the way of the ninja!

662
00:51:10.708 --> 00:51:12.542
- That's Japanese.
- Right.

663
00:51:13.708 --> 00:51:18.167
Anyone who breaks the rules
in the ninja world

664
00:51:18.250 --> 00:51:20.417
is trash!

665
00:51:20.500 --> 00:51:22.625
Trash!

666
00:51:23.792 --> 00:51:24.792
Your turn.

667
00:51:26.292 --> 00:51:32.042
But someone who betrays their friends
is worse than trash!

668
00:51:36.458 --> 00:51:38.667
Made, do you wanna try it too?

669
00:51:40.000 --> 00:51:41.917
- Come on.
- Do it, Made!

670
00:51:42.000 --> 00:51:43.583
Made!

671
00:51:47.500 --> 00:51:48.750
Let's go.

672
00:51:52.292 --> 00:51:53.792
Let's do it in Indonesian.

673
00:51:54.458 --> 00:51:55.458
Okay.

674
00:51:59.000 --> 00:52:04.250
I love ramen noodles!

675
00:52:07.458 --> 00:52:12.208
I love ramen noodles!

676
00:52:15.417 --> 00:52:16.708
Wonderful.

677
00:52:17.375 --> 00:52:22.292
Made, in Japan, they would definitely
love to watch wayang puppetry.

678
00:52:22.875 --> 00:52:24.417
- Very good.
- Very good.

679
00:52:26.083 --> 00:52:27.083
My manager.

680
00:52:27.167 --> 00:52:30.708
- I think he's considering a career switch.
- Really?

681
00:52:30.792 --> 00:52:33.625
He doesn't want to be
a puppeteer anymore. Am I right?

682
00:52:42.167 --> 00:52:46.000
It's okay. We can
discuss it again in Jakarta.

683
00:52:48.125 --> 00:52:51.083
- You're set on moving to Jakarta?
- Of course.

684
00:52:51.750 --> 00:52:53.375
I have a career in Jakarta.

685
00:52:54.375 --> 00:52:57.917
It doesn't make sense for him
to stay here when I'm in Jakarta.

686
00:54:15.917 --> 00:54:19.500
<i>I wish Putu had never told me
about Niluh's feelings for me.</i>

687
00:54:19.583 --> 00:54:22.083
<i>I wouldn't be so conflicted.</i>

688
00:54:47.708 --> 00:54:51.417
<i>I wish her feelings for me
had remained hidden.</i>

689
00:54:52.208 --> 00:54:54.500
<i>She could've gone back
to Japan without a worry.</i>

690
00:54:55.708 --> 00:54:57.542
<i>And I could move on with my life.</i>

691
00:54:57.625 --> 00:54:58.875
ACCEPTED

692
00:54:58.958 --> 00:55:03.333
<i>Like nothing had happened between us.</i>

693
00:55:05.292 --> 00:55:08.375
<i>Because there is nothing
going on between us.</i>

694
00:55:08.500 --> 00:55:15.333
<i>I wish she had no feelings for me,
and that I felt the same.</i>

695
00:55:23.042 --> 00:55:25.542
I got rejected by Dewata University

696
00:55:29.750 --> 00:55:34.250
<i>Please tell me I don't
have feelings for her too.</i>

697
00:57:04.042 --> 00:57:08.333
<i>Or maybe everybody
already knew how I felt about her.</i>

698
00:57:09.167 --> 00:57:11.917
<i>Everybody, including Shiro.</i>

699
00:57:13.042 --> 00:57:17.000
<i>Maybe I was the last one to know.</i>

700
00:57:21.208 --> 00:57:27.542
<i>And how do you express your feelings
for someone who knows you inside out,</i>

701
00:57:28.375 --> 00:57:31.000
<i>including your tendency to throw up?</i>

702
00:57:31.625 --> 00:57:37.917
<i>What if, right after I told her
that I love her, she threw up?</i>

703
00:58:06.875 --> 00:58:09.542
<i>So I decided to tell her
in a more indirect way.</i>

704
00:58:10.708 --> 00:58:12.208
<i>A way that I know.</i>

705
00:58:12.958 --> 00:58:14.125
<i>Using wayang puppetry.</i>

706
00:58:33.083 --> 00:58:34.208
Hey, Made, what's up?

707
00:58:35.125 --> 00:58:36.208
Do you need anything?

708
00:58:36.792 --> 00:58:40.750
I want to surprise someone.

709
00:58:41.708 --> 00:58:42.917
How can I help?

710
00:58:46.042 --> 00:58:50.625
Could you please translate this
into Japanese before Niluh leaves?

711
00:59:09.083 --> 00:59:10.583
May you be blessed.

712
00:59:10.667 --> 00:59:12.542
May you be blessed too.

713
00:59:14.583 --> 00:59:17.708
Can you make some leather puppets for me?

714
00:59:17.792 --> 00:59:19.208
Do you have the drawings?

715
00:59:19.292 --> 00:59:21.250
Yes, I have the drawings.

716
00:59:24.917 --> 00:59:29.333
<i>And like so many times
in my life, I lied again.</i>

717
00:59:29.417 --> 00:59:31.917
- Why in a Japanese style?
- I want it to be unique.

718
00:59:32.000 --> 00:59:36.167
<i>One day, my lies will eventually
catch up with me like karma.</i>

719
00:59:39.708 --> 00:59:44.458
<i>But for now, let me lie.</i>

720
00:59:52.167 --> 00:59:53.417
Mom! I'm going.

721
00:59:53.500 --> 00:59:54.667
Where are you going?

722
00:59:57.125 --> 00:59:58.125
Made!

723
01:00:00.667 --> 01:00:02.000
Where is he going?

724
01:00:02.083 --> 01:00:04.375
I don't know. He seems very busy.

725
01:00:07.708 --> 01:00:11.625
- And he's been acting strangely too.
- Is he going out with Niluh?

726
01:00:15.042 --> 01:00:18.667
<i>I wrote the storyline.
I also wrote the music.</i>

727
01:00:18.750 --> 01:00:19.750
Once upon a time…

728
01:00:19.792 --> 01:00:21.792
<i>Now I have to memorize the narration.</i>

729
01:00:21.875 --> 01:00:23.708
Not <i>"musashi,"</i> it's <i>"mukashi."</i>

730
01:00:23.792 --> 01:00:27.333
<i>And it seems like this will be
the most tangled love confession.</i>

731
01:00:27.417 --> 01:00:28.833
<i>As tangled as my tongue.</i>

732
01:00:32.250 --> 01:00:34.750
Musashi was the name
of a Japanese samurai.

733
01:00:34.833 --> 01:00:36.500
A samurai.

734
01:01:07.375 --> 01:01:12.542
Rama and Sinta met…

735
01:01:18.292 --> 01:01:21.667
When they were little…

736
01:01:26.250 --> 01:01:28.042
When they were…

737
01:01:28.625 --> 01:01:32.042
Still little…

738
01:01:32.125 --> 01:01:33.375
Children…

739
01:01:34.542 --> 01:01:35.542
Not <i>"komodo."</i>

740
01:01:36.708 --> 01:01:38.708
Not <i>"komodo."</i> It's <i>"kodomo."</i>

741
01:01:38.792 --> 01:01:40.625
Not <i>"komodo." "Kodomo."</i>

742
01:01:45.833 --> 01:01:49.625
Hey, get me a bottle of sake!

743
01:02:04.417 --> 01:02:05.583
They're beautiful!

744
01:02:11.167 --> 01:02:13.333
Putu came here the other day.

745
01:02:14.292 --> 01:02:16.833
She said she saw you
going into my workshop.

746
01:02:18.250 --> 01:02:21.917
She asked me what you were doing here.

747
01:02:26.292 --> 01:02:30.833
But I didn't tell her you were here
to commission leather puppets.

748
01:02:33.167 --> 01:02:35.125
Great. Thank you, sir!

749
01:02:35.875 --> 01:02:37.500
- I'll go now, sir.
- Sure.

750
01:02:48.333 --> 01:02:49.333
Made.

751
01:02:52.667 --> 01:02:54.708
Are you from Nuarta's workshop?

752
01:02:54.792 --> 01:02:56.750
<i>- There she is.</i>
- Did you order puppets?

753
01:02:57.417 --> 01:03:00.042
- Who are they for?
<i>- It seems like karma</i>

754
01:03:00.125 --> 01:03:01.750
<i>is finally catching up to me.</i>

755
01:03:07.625 --> 01:03:08.792
It's for a souvenir.

756
01:03:11.125 --> 01:03:13.167
Why didn't you ask my father to make them?

757
01:03:14.667 --> 01:03:16.000
I need them fast.

758
01:03:17.500 --> 01:03:20.583
I don't want to rush your dad.

759
01:03:22.208 --> 01:03:23.833
I see. Okay.

760
01:03:25.167 --> 01:03:26.208
I'll see you later.

761
01:03:26.833 --> 01:03:29.042
- I'm having a photo session.
- Okay.

762
01:03:31.958 --> 01:03:34.458
I know who you're planning
to gift that to.

763
01:03:38.042 --> 01:03:39.875
Bye. Take care.

764
01:03:49.625 --> 01:03:52.333
CONSULATE GENERAL OF JAPAN

765
01:03:53.875 --> 01:03:54.875
Thank you.

766
01:03:59.958 --> 01:04:05.458
Gosh, our visa applications
are finally approved!

767
01:04:05.542 --> 01:04:06.542
Yeah.

768
01:04:12.292 --> 01:04:14.000
I promised her.

769
01:04:17.083 --> 01:04:18.125
Ichika<i>-chan.</i>

770
01:04:20.792 --> 01:04:21.792
Yes, Dad?

771
01:04:23.708 --> 01:04:27.125
Yesterday, Made came to see us

772
01:04:28.417 --> 01:04:31.542
and he talked to us.

773
01:04:35.625 --> 01:04:39.667
He has something for you.

774
01:04:40.542 --> 01:04:43.792
SHINTA GOES TO JAPAN

775
01:04:57.917 --> 01:05:02.833
He just wants to say goodbye to her.

776
01:05:05.292 --> 01:05:07.250
That kid means nothing to me.

777
01:05:08.375 --> 01:05:13.500
I just don't want our baby
to get hurt even more.

778
01:05:21.292 --> 01:05:25.958
I know what you've been busy with lately.

779
01:05:29.292 --> 01:05:31.083
What show are you planning for Niluh?

780
01:05:34.333 --> 01:05:36.583
It's just a little farewell party.

781
01:05:38.542 --> 01:05:40.250
It was supposed to be a secret too.

782
01:05:41.958 --> 01:05:43.542
Does Putu know about your plan?

783
01:05:45.292 --> 01:05:46.333
No, Mom.

784
01:05:46.417 --> 01:05:48.833
Are you considering
Putu's feelings at all?

785
01:05:51.917 --> 01:05:53.250
I don't agree with it.

786
01:05:53.958 --> 01:05:55.167
Don't carry on with it.

787
01:05:56.542 --> 01:06:00.375
- Mom, it's just a gift to a friend.
- Just a friend?

788
01:06:01.042 --> 01:06:02.042
Are you sure?

789
01:06:04.333 --> 01:06:09.750
Trust me, if you go forward with this,
it will ruin your karma with Putu.

790
01:06:17.583 --> 01:06:21.708
Your betrothal has been planned
for a long time.

791
01:06:23.125 --> 01:06:25.125
It involves two large families.

792
01:06:26.458 --> 01:06:29.250
It involves our respect
as wayang puppeteers.

793
01:06:32.792 --> 01:06:34.875
Why are you being so reckless now?

794
01:06:38.167 --> 01:06:40.250
It's just a small show, Dad.

795
01:06:53.000 --> 01:06:57.750
Sang Hyang Widi knows the truth
behind every word we speak.

796
01:07:00.000 --> 01:07:06.292
Your mother and I, as your parents,
we have already warned you.

797
01:07:08.625 --> 01:07:11.042
But if you insist on doing it…

798
01:07:14.333 --> 01:07:17.875
I will leave the decision to the universe.

799
01:07:30.000 --> 01:07:32.833
<i>First of all, we apologize.</i>

800
01:07:34.417 --> 01:07:39.083
<i>The reason we came here is…</i>

801
01:07:39.167 --> 01:07:40.250
<i>Forgive me.</i>

802
01:07:41.542 --> 01:07:42.958
<i>Sir. Ma'am.</i>

803
01:07:47.625 --> 01:07:50.667
<i>I just want to express my true feelings.</i>

804
01:07:56.083 --> 01:08:01.250
I also want to apologize
if I haven't been truthful with Putu.

805
01:08:02.667 --> 01:08:05.250
I tried so hard to love you.

806
01:08:07.000 --> 01:08:11.500
But love never reached my heart.

807
01:08:14.542 --> 01:08:15.833
What do you mean, De?

808
01:08:16.792 --> 01:08:18.333
Forgive me, ma'am.

809
01:08:21.708 --> 01:08:24.833
I am here to ask for your permission…

810
01:08:27.042 --> 01:08:30.208
To withdraw from this betrothal.

811
01:08:52.208 --> 01:08:53.500
Do you understand…

812
01:08:55.875 --> 01:08:59.125
That the betrothal is a sacred thing?

813
01:09:01.417 --> 01:09:03.833
And it cannot be undone by anyone's will?

814
01:09:08.292 --> 01:09:09.292
Now…

815
01:09:10.542 --> 01:09:13.417
What do you think, Mr. Ketut?

816
01:09:14.417 --> 01:09:17.417
Sorry for not being able to honor
this betrothal commitment.

817
01:09:20.208 --> 01:09:23.583
Because it turns out,
when it comes to the feeling of love

818
01:09:25.125 --> 01:09:28.583
and finding your match,

819
01:09:29.583 --> 01:09:31.917
it's not up to us to decide.

820
01:09:32.458 --> 01:09:36.125
These are beyond our control.

821
01:09:37.625 --> 01:09:43.125
Only Hyang Widi can make that decision.

822
01:09:54.375 --> 01:09:57.292
What are your thoughts, Putu?

823
01:09:59.250 --> 01:10:00.583
I have no choice, Mom.

824
01:10:01.625 --> 01:10:06.833
If this betrothal is cancelled,
he'll be the one who's going to regret it.

825
01:10:09.792 --> 01:10:11.417
Let him face his karma.

826
01:10:33.583 --> 01:10:38.042
<i>The closer it gets to her leaving,
the more everything sinks in.</i>

827
01:10:38.750 --> 01:10:41.083
<i>And it increasingly feels like a dream.</i>

828
01:11:16.917 --> 01:11:18.625
<i>But I won't back down.</i>

829
01:11:19.583 --> 01:11:21.750
<i>Whatever will be, will be.</i>

830
01:11:34.750 --> 01:11:38.917
Niluh, I planned this show
because you're leaving.

831
01:11:40.125 --> 01:11:46.250
Consider this as a parting gift
and a goodbye.

832
01:11:47.750 --> 01:11:48.750
To you.

833
01:11:55.958 --> 01:11:57.958
This place is better than I thought.

834
01:12:07.125 --> 01:12:09.875
Are these the wayang puppets you ordered?

835
01:12:25.667 --> 01:12:28.292
I don't want to spoil your show.

836
01:12:31.250 --> 01:12:35.500
But I just want to see
what caused the breakup of our engagement.

837
01:13:35.167 --> 01:13:37.167
In the kingdom of Kosala…

838
01:13:39.458 --> 01:13:43.625
King Dasaratha and Queen Kausalya

839
01:13:44.250 --> 01:13:47.958
had a firstborn son named Sang Rama.

840
01:13:49.000 --> 01:13:53.625
He was an incarnation of the god Vishnu.

841
01:13:57.708 --> 01:13:59.708
In the kingdom of Mantili,

842
01:13:59.792 --> 01:14:04.667
King Janaka had a daughter
named Dewi Sinta.

843
01:14:05.458 --> 01:14:10.750
Rama and Sinta were a divine couple.

844
01:14:13.250 --> 01:14:18.042
The incarnation of the god Vishnu
and the goddess Widowati.

845
01:14:33.042 --> 01:14:36.208
Once upon a time…

846
01:14:39.083 --> 01:14:42.917
Rama and Sinta met.

847
01:14:45.042 --> 01:14:48.750
When they were little,

848
01:14:48.833 --> 01:14:55.375
they fell in love with each other.

849
01:14:55.458 --> 01:14:58.750
But never realized it
until they were teenagers.

850
01:15:00.792 --> 01:15:04.208
One day, Sinta was

851
01:15:05.375 --> 01:15:08.417
kidnapped by Rahwana.

852
01:15:13.500 --> 01:15:17.292
And he took her to a land

853
01:15:17.375 --> 01:15:23.042
where her little starling companion
couldn't go.

854
01:15:23.125 --> 01:15:29.500
Rama didn't know
if he'd ever meet Sinta again.

855
01:15:30.375 --> 01:15:34.583
But this was
his declaration of love to Sinta.

856
01:15:35.208 --> 01:15:39.625
By letting her fly away
like she did to the starling.

857
01:15:39.708 --> 01:15:44.208
In a hope, wherever Sinta went,
wherever she stayed,

858
01:15:44.292 --> 01:15:46.625
her heart would remain here forever.

859
01:15:48.458 --> 01:15:50.208
The kingdom of Alengka is destroyed.

860
01:15:50.292 --> 01:15:52.792
The ruins lay beneath Rama's feet.

861
01:15:59.250 --> 01:16:03.042
Rahwana was defeated,
with an arrow stuck in his chest.

862
01:16:10.542 --> 01:16:16.792
Rama and Sinta together again,
standing in a beam of light.

863
01:16:18.667 --> 01:16:25.208
Finally, Rama and Sinta
returned to the realm of Nirvana.

864
01:16:39.458 --> 01:16:43.292
<i>So whatever will be, will be.</i>

865
01:17:05.625 --> 01:17:06.792
Niluh!

866
01:17:06.875 --> 01:17:09.417
Why are you in such a hurry?

867
01:17:09.500 --> 01:17:11.083
Come on, I'll give you a ride.

868
01:17:11.167 --> 01:17:13.333
Thanks, I can get home on my own.

869
01:17:14.208 --> 01:17:16.042
You can go home with Keiko.

870
01:17:21.417 --> 01:17:22.417
You're still here?

871
01:17:23.208 --> 01:17:24.208
So what?

872
01:17:37.667 --> 01:17:39.042
What are you doing here?

873
01:17:40.250 --> 01:17:42.083
I don't understand Japanese.

874
01:17:46.125 --> 01:17:49.292
But I understand Made's body language.

875
01:17:50.625 --> 01:17:56.667
I could choose any man to be my boyfriend.

876
01:17:56.750 --> 01:18:02.500
But I value my commitment
to my parents more.

877
01:18:06.625 --> 01:18:07.708
Now I understand…

878
01:18:10.208 --> 01:18:14.917
Why he couldn't keep the same commitment.

879
01:18:20.375 --> 01:18:22.625
Because he's loved you all along.

880
01:18:30.083 --> 01:18:35.750
Both of you have passed the friend zone.

881
01:18:37.250 --> 01:18:40.958
And disrespected
the commitment of our parents.

882
01:18:49.958 --> 01:18:55.250
So now,
I'm excited that you're finally leaving.

883
01:19:00.667 --> 01:19:04.292
Because all this time…

884
01:19:07.042 --> 01:19:10.333
You've only been an obstacle
in my relationship with Made.

885
01:19:42.458 --> 01:19:43.625
Go after her.

886
01:19:43.708 --> 01:19:46.333
This is your last chance.
Your final moments.

887
01:19:50.958 --> 01:19:51.958
Go after her.

888
01:19:59.250 --> 01:20:00.250
Made.

889
01:20:04.167 --> 01:20:05.833
Think again.

890
01:20:09.250 --> 01:20:14.833
About everything you've fought for
by following your heart.

891
01:20:22.708 --> 01:20:23.708
Me.

892
01:20:25.875 --> 01:20:27.167
Our future.

893
01:20:28.708 --> 01:20:29.875
Our dreams.

894
01:20:34.542 --> 01:20:37.208
Are you sure you want
to cancel our betrothal…

895
01:20:39.500 --> 01:20:41.958
That we've built together?

896
01:20:45.958 --> 01:20:48.083
Do you want to leave me for her?

897
01:20:53.958 --> 01:20:55.167
Forgive me.

898
01:21:01.208 --> 01:21:03.708
I haven't been honest
with my feelings all this time.

899
01:21:06.375 --> 01:21:08.958
I tried to fall in love with you.

900
01:21:11.208 --> 01:21:13.250
But the truth is, my heart said otherwise.

901
01:21:19.542 --> 01:21:24.250
I tried to follow your dream.

902
01:21:28.125 --> 01:21:30.000
But going to Jakarta is not my dream.

903
01:21:32.125 --> 01:21:33.125
So what now?

904
01:21:38.500 --> 01:21:40.000
Pursue your dreams.

905
01:21:44.208 --> 01:21:45.750
And I'll pursue mine.

906
01:22:41.542 --> 01:22:45.458
- Dad, where's Mom?
- She's already in the car.

907
01:22:46.333 --> 01:22:49.375
Our stuff has also been
taken by the delivery truck.

908
01:22:50.208 --> 01:22:51.208
Let's go.

909
01:24:31.250 --> 01:24:32.500
Kadek! Wayan!

910
01:24:33.875 --> 01:24:35.458
Let's catch up with Niluh.

911
01:24:35.542 --> 01:24:36.958
Didn't you meet her?

912
01:24:37.042 --> 01:24:38.583
Her taxi just left.

913
01:24:38.667 --> 01:24:39.958
Why didn't you tell me?

914
01:24:40.042 --> 01:24:41.583
How should we know?

915
01:24:42.708 --> 01:24:45.583
All right, let's go to the airport now.
Come on.

916
01:24:45.667 --> 01:24:47.625
How are you going to get there?

917
01:24:47.708 --> 01:24:50.125
On your bike? Can you catch up to her?

918
01:24:55.417 --> 01:24:57.333
No. On this wagon.

919
01:24:58.792 --> 01:24:59.833
Are you sure?

920
01:24:59.917 --> 01:25:03.042
- You won't feel nauseous?
- No. I can manage.

921
01:25:15.000 --> 01:25:16.000
Step on it!

922
01:25:29.542 --> 01:25:34.500
Hopefully, there won't be
any obstacles whatsoever.

923
01:25:47.792 --> 01:25:52.250
<i>My father always said,
every person is born with their karma.</i>

924
01:25:53.042 --> 01:25:56.833
<i>Every event in our lives is connected</i>

925
01:25:56.917 --> 01:26:00.708
<i>by choices and decisions we make.</i>

926
01:26:11.542 --> 01:26:13.625
I can't take it anymore.

927
01:26:13.708 --> 01:26:15.208
You'll ruin your clothes…

928
01:26:15.292 --> 01:26:18.458
<i>Up to this point,
everything has been decided for me.</i>

929
01:26:18.542 --> 01:26:22.333
<i>But this time, I choose my own path.</i>

930
01:26:22.417 --> 01:26:25.708
<i>I have to see
where this road will take me.</i>

931
01:26:26.500 --> 01:26:28.583
We're more than just friends.

932
01:26:32.458 --> 01:26:36.125
Because my feelings for you
go far beyond that.

933
01:26:42.667 --> 01:26:46.083
And I've been lying to myself

934
01:26:46.792 --> 01:26:49.708
because I know you're betrothed to Putu.

935
01:26:55.500 --> 01:26:56.875
<i>We share the same feelings.</i>

936
01:27:00.000 --> 01:27:01.708
We share the same feelings.

937
01:27:02.333 --> 01:27:04.833
I haven't been honest
with my feelings all this time…

938
01:27:06.208 --> 01:27:07.208
Because I was afraid.

939
01:27:08.875 --> 01:27:10.833
I was afraid of losing you.

940
01:27:19.500 --> 01:27:20.958
Are you okay?

941
01:27:22.792 --> 01:27:24.000
I'm fine, Mom.

942
01:27:44.750 --> 01:27:45.958
Niluh, pull over!

943
01:28:06.583 --> 01:28:07.583
Made.

944
01:28:09.292 --> 01:28:11.000
Did you just ride in that wagon?

945
01:28:13.208 --> 01:28:14.583
I'm doing this for you.

946
01:28:16.000 --> 01:28:18.250
How could you leave
without saying goodbye?

947
01:28:21.917 --> 01:28:23.583
And why did you leave this?

948
01:28:24.958 --> 01:28:27.792
- Do you really want to forget me?
- What more do you want?

949
01:28:28.458 --> 01:28:31.208
Isn't it enough
that your girlfriend embarrassed me?

950
01:28:33.417 --> 01:28:35.083
We were betrothed.

951
01:28:36.875 --> 01:28:38.875
But Putu is not my girlfriend.

952
01:28:41.750 --> 01:28:43.458
And I love you.

953
01:28:45.167 --> 01:28:49.542
Do you remember when you freed
the starling from its cage?

954
01:28:50.292 --> 01:28:51.583
I've just realized that

955
01:28:52.542 --> 01:28:55.292
I've locked away
my feelings for you all this time.

956
01:29:05.000 --> 01:29:06.750
Just like that starling.

957
01:29:11.208 --> 01:29:12.708
But now, they're flying free.

958
01:29:16.917 --> 01:29:21.333
And one day, they will fly there.

959
01:29:24.833 --> 01:29:26.083
To catch up with you.

960
01:30:03.333 --> 01:30:04.333
Niluh!

961
01:30:08.292 --> 01:30:09.833
Farewell, Mukudori<i>-chan!</i>

962
01:30:50.542 --> 01:30:53.125
<i>Our paths finally parted.</i>

963
01:30:54.083 --> 01:30:57.875
<i>I don't know
if it's for a while or forever.</i>

964
01:31:24.708 --> 01:31:29.375
<i>But one day, I will walk this path again.</i>

965
01:31:30.250 --> 01:31:31.250
<i>The same road.</i>

966
01:31:32.208 --> 01:31:35.542
<i>So I can see where it leads.</i>

967
01:32:04.667 --> 01:32:07.000
- Good morning, Ichika.
- Good morning.

968
01:32:12.792 --> 01:32:14.083
You may start.

969
01:32:15.292 --> 01:32:16.875
Yes, I understand.

970
01:32:19.750 --> 01:32:20.750
Okay!

